        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Victims Of Immigration Crime Engagement Restoration Act or as the VOICE Restoration Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Victims of Immigration Crime Engagement Office within U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement. The office shall provide assistance to victims of crimes committed by non-U.S. nationals (<i>aliens</i> under federal law) who are present in the United States without lawful immigration status. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
